longBusinessSummary: PT Fajar Surya Wisesa Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells packaging papers in Indonesia, East Africa, the Middle East, and rest of Asia. The company offers coated duplex boards for use in light-weight packaging materials for pharmaceutical products, shoes, household goods, processed foods, and consumer electronics. It also provides container board products, such as brown packaging paper that is used for the outer layers of corrugated sheets; fluting papers for the construction of carton boxes; and white liner boards for industrial packaging and box making. The company sells its products directly to industrial and consumer goods manufacturing companies. The company was founded in 1987 and is based in Jakarta Pusat, Indonesia. PT Fajar Surya Wisesa Tbk is a subsidiary of SCGP Solutions (Singapore) Pte. Ltd.
